dithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-hundred-years\/","url_meta":{"origin":23257,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah distances him from Hell by 100 years","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, Allah will distance him from Hell by a measure of one hundred years of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2254 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39756,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/angels-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":23257,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Allah and angels bless the pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who eat before fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3467 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28099,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-seventy-autumns\/","url_meta":{"origin":23257,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah delivers him from Hell by seventy autumns","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, by that day Allah will deliver his face from the Hellfire a distance of seventy autumns of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2244 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5253,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/17\/fasting-ramadan-six-days-shawwal\/","url_meta":{"origin":23257,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Six more days of Shawwal like fasting a year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting the month of Ramadan is like ten months of fasting and fasting six days of Shawwal is like two months of fasting. Thus, they are like fasting for a year.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2115 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\